traits.locale_text: [Драфт] "Слишком много голосов... Я слышу их ярость. "Дверь открыта — иди, отомсти за нас", — говорят они".

languages.text: "Too many voices... I can hear their rage. 'The door is open — come and avenge us,' they say."

languages.text: "Zu viele Stimmen ... Ich kann ihren Zorn hören. 'Die Tür steht offen — kommt und rächt uns', sagen sie."
languages.original_text: "Too many voices... I can hear their rage. 'The door is open — come and avenge us,' they say."

traits.locale_text: "Zu viele Stimmen ... Ich kann ihren Zorn hören. 'Die Tür steht offen — kommt und rächt uns', sagen sie.

languages.text: « Toutes ces voix... J'entends leur furie. "La porte est ouverte, venez nous venger," elles disent. »
languages.original_text: "Too many voices... I can hear their rage. 'The door is open — come and avenge us,' they say."

traits.locale_text: « Toutes ces voix... J'entends leur furie. "La porte est ouverte, venez nous venger," elles disent. »

languages.text: “声音太多了……我听到了他们的愤怒。‘门开了，快来为我们报仇吧’——他们是这么说的。”
languages.original_text: "Too many voices... I can hear their rage. 'The door is open — come and avenge us,' they say."

traits.locale_text: “声音太多了……我听到了他们的愤怒。‘门开了，快来为我们报仇吧’——他们是这么说的。”

languages.text: 「声が多すぎる…彼らの怒りが聞こえるわ。『扉は開いた、仇を討ちに来い』ってね」
languages.original_text: "Too many voices... I can hear their rage. 'The door is open — come and avenge us,' they say."

traits.locale_text: 「いくつもの声が…彼らの怒りが聞こえるわ。『扉は開いた、仇を討ちに来い』だそうよ」
「声が多すぎる…彼らの怒りが聞こえるわ。『扉は開いた、仇を討ちに来い』ってね」

languages.text: "Çok fazla ses var... Öfkelerini duyabiliyorum. 'Kapı açık, gel ve intikamımızı al' diyorlar."
